data.description: Don't let the Maysville address fool ya! This charming 4 bedroom 2 bath double wide is just minutes from Piney Green Road and is close proximity to Camp Lejeune, dining and shopping. More than 2000 heated square feet with a split bedroom floor plan and plenty of living space. Laminate flooring throughout and a privacy fenced back yard. Garden tub and separate shower in the master suite. Must see this home today!
